snippet.title: Har Karam Apna Karenge | Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge | Hindi Desh Bhakti Song | Karma (1986)
snippet.description:
Song Details :
Star Cast: Dilip Kumar, Nutan, Naseeruddin Shah, Jackie Shroff, Anil Kapoor, Anupam Kher, Sridevi, Poonam Dhillon
Singers: Mohammad Aziz, Kavita Krishnamurthy
Music Director:  Laxmikant Pyarelal
Lyrics by: Anand Bakshi
Producer & Director: Subhash Ghai

Lyrics:
Mera Karma Tu Mera Dharma Tu 
Tera Sab Kuch Main Mera Sab Kuch Tu
Har Karam Apna Karenge
Har Karam Apna Karenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Har Karam Apna Karenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Har Karam Apna Karenge Aye Watan Tere Liye


Tu Mera Karma Tu Mera Dharma Tu Mera Abhiman Hai
Aye Watan Mehboob Mere Tujhpe Dil Kurban Hai
Aye Watan Mehboob Mere Tujhpe Dil Kurban Hai
Hum Jiyenge Aur Marenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye

Hindu Muslim Sikh Isayi Hum Watan Hum Naam Hai
Hindu Muslim Sikh Isayi Hum Watan Hum Naam Hai
Jo Kare Inko Juda Mazhab Nahi Ilzam Hai
Hum Jiyenge Aur Marenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jaan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye

Teri Galiyon Mein Chala Kar Nafraton Ki Goliya
Loot Te Hai Kuch Lutere Dulhano Ki Doliyan
Loot Rahe Hai Aap Woh Apne Gharon Ko Loot Kar
Khelte Hai Bekhabar Apne Lahu Se Holiya
Hum Jiyenge Aur Marenge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye
Dil Diya Hai Jan Bhi Denge Aye Watan Tere Liye

YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. snippet.title: Maa Jaye - Trailer | Jimmy Sheirgill | Manav Vij | Yograj Singh | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
From the makers of heartfelt Punjabi cinema comes a story of Brothers love, sacrifice, and unbreakable bonds. Maa Jaye follows the journey of Brotherhood, family, and the struggles that test the limits of relationships.

"Maa Jaye" in cinemas on 29th August 2025.

Starring - Jimmy Sheirgill, Manav Vij, Yograj Singh
Introducing - Rehmat Rattan

Producer - Dr Amarjit Singh
Director - Navaniat Singh

Screenplay Adaptation - Inderpal Singh
Dialogues and Additional Screenplay - Gurpreet Sehji
Music - Jaidev Kumar
Cinematographer - Jitan Harmeet Singh
Editor - Rohit Dhiman

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: The Great Shinobi War  | Academy Trials Day 1 #freefire #gyangaming #freefirelive
snippet.description:
The Great Shinobi War  | Academy Trials Day 1 #freefire #gyangaming #freefirelive 

Schedule
Date : 14 AUG 2025
IDP Time : 08:00 PM 
START Time : 08:10 PM

Participating Teams :

GROUP KONOHAGAKURE

NG PROS
KV18 ESPORTS 
VASIYO ESPORTS 
RNX ESPORTS 
DESI ESPORTS 
SARKAR
TEAM ELITE
RG ARMY
Ahmed Gaming
Ebuus Era
EG OFFICIALS 
FULL MOON



Prizepool - 10,000 INR
Team Distribution & Grouping

48 Total Teams:

- 24 from Partner Program
- 12 from Extended Program
- 12 from Open Qualifiers

4 Groups of 12 Teams each:

- Konohagakure (Hidden Leaf Village)
- Sunagakure (Hidden Sand Village)
- Kirigakure (Hidden Mist Village)
- Kumogakure (Hidden Cloud Village)

Tournament Format & Roadmap


Stages & Details:

Academy Trials

- 4 Groups (12 teams each)
- 6 matches per group
- Top 6 teams from each group qualify


Ninja Vanguard

- 2 Groups (12 teams each)
- 6 matches per group
- Top 6 teams from each group qualify


Great Shinobi War (Grand Finals)

- 12 Final teams
- 12 matches in a 1-day grand final
- Winner crowned champion


Shinobi Reckoning (Clash Squad Showdown)

- Top 8 teams from Grand Finals
- Quarterfinals: Best of 1 matches
- Semifinals: Best of 3 matches
- Finals: Best of 5 matches

Tournament Timeline

- Day 1 (14 August): Academy Trials ‚Äì Group Konohagakure (Hidden Leaf Village)
- Day 2 (15 August): Academy Trials ‚Äì Group Sunagakure (Hidden Sand Village)
- Day 3 (16 August): Academy Trials ‚Äì Group Kirigakure (Hidden Mist Village)
- Day 4 (17 August): Academy Trials ‚Äì Group Kumogakure (Hidden Cloud Village)
- Day 5 (18 August): Ninja Vanguard ‚Äì Group A
- Day 6 (19 August): Ninja Vanguard ‚Äì Group B
- Day 7 (20 August): Great Shinobi War ‚Äì Grand Finals
- Day 8 (21 August): Shinobi Reckoning ‚Äì Clash Squad Showdown

Prize Pool Distribution

Total Prize Pool: 3,00,000 Diamonds

- Champion: 1,20,000 Diamonds
- Runner-Up: 50,000 Diamonds
- Second Runner-Up: 30,000 Diamonds
- Most Valuable Player (MVP): 20,000 Diamonds
- Clash Squad Winner: 80,000 Diamonds

Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:
* Monday Tamil Devotional Songs

* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.
* Saibaba Tamil Devotional Songs: Seek the blessings of Shirdi Sai Baba.

* Devi Tamil Devotional Songs: Praise the supreme goddess Devi in her many avatars.
* Ganesh Tamil Devotional Songs: Start your day with prayers to Lord Ganesha.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.
* Ashta Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs dedicated to the eight forms of Goddess Lakshmi.
* Vinayagar Tamil Devotional Songs: Devotions for the remover of obstacles, Lord Vinayagar.
* Ganapathi Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke blessings from Lord Ganapathi.
* Surya Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship the Sun God, Surya, with these melodies.
* Sani Tamil Devotional Songs: Appease Lord Sani with these devotional tracks.
* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

Subscribe now and join our spiritual journey. Like, share, and hit the bell icon to stay updated with our latest devotional uploads. May these divine songs bring peace, prosperity, and positivity to your life.
